description:
Harajuku`s been turned into a safari park?! Giraffe, alligator, and zebra shaped Scoopers have begun wandering around town. When a single bird comes flying into PARK, Misa attempts to chase it away, but right before her eyes the color is stolen right out of some beads. Rito and friends hurry after the bird, but the color has been stolen from all over town.
Source: crunchyroll
